an example others should follow to help rid housing projects of 
drugs and gangs 
the omaha agency adopted the policy last week arming itself 
with the power to evict tenants who themselves or whose children or 
other household members including guests are suspected of 
certain crimes 
kemp last week announced hud actions aimed at easing the 
eviction process for local agencies that operate federally 
subsidized housing projects among other things hud is making drug 
offenses a specific violation of leases 
last month alexandria va mayor james p moran secured a 
